Wijnaldum: At half-time the manager said I must get into the box more. Emre was in the box a few times &amp; he said I wasn&rsquo;t in the box once.&quot;<br />
<br />
Wijnaldum: &quot;We showed it against the big teams, but now we must show it against every team. Then it will say more than only today.&quot;

Klopp: &quot;We've won lot of games against these kind of teams. We lost 3 to what you would call 'weaker'. It's down to us, not them.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;Even when you are a perfect side, and we're not, you will lose football games. But we've proved often enough that we know the way.&quot;

Klopp: &quot;This club has an outstanding power if we keep our nerve. &quot;#LFC<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;We have improved a lot but so have other teams. The fight for something is always tight and intense.&quot;
